{"tid":1286820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢只係維權, 唔會令中國亂","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:33:59.000Z","uid":66784,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb51bf015fc8d9be51994b27a402b840c10d2c8","tid":1286820,"uid":66784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"我見到隔離post條友講到支持武漢係為咗令中國亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286566\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286566</a><br />\n<br />\n實在太天真，武漢呢種只係維權，本質上同中國古代老百姓擊鼓嗚冤冇分別<br />\n潛台詞都係: 最衰都係貪官，皇帝係最英明<br />\n唔好話反中，連共都唔反，叫武漢人做大中華都太抬舉佢地<br />\n<br />\n你話佢地可以增加中國政府管治成本？佢地連烏坎村一半都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加成本條毛<br />\n<br />\n中國政府勢力範圍內，叫做似樣嘅抗爭，只有西藏新疆同香港，你要支持就支持呢幾個，得呢三個地方先可以大量消耗統戰維穩經費<br />\n<br />\n再唔係支持雲南邊境毒販，伊斯蘭教同基督教，甚至法輪功<br />\n都有用過支持武漢反對興建焚化爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1999471eceec3041be9a60951a092ba32066cad","tid":1286820,"uid":153722,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"咪撚再幫武漢開post"},{"pid":"eb61c50d4356ec11bbd2ef114ffb2e4a46d351a1","tid":1286820,"uid":257422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"大佬香港國際城市本身就係同外國有經濟政治關係，同武漢邊撚度一樣！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">你聲援武漢外國一撚定唔知你講乜鳩，根本無人care依個地方！包括支那人自己都唔care! 聲你老母援咩？</span> </span>"},{"pid":"d26763ab35cbb7f73781e9ad99bb3bd0bf1cc633","tid":1286820,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:36:43.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30b44442bc253fa42d1b9968590d5535e1e9288a","tid":1286820,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"仲嘈緊武漢一事既巴打 記住只係 &quot;聲&quot; 援<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/deBGAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/deBGAS</a><br />\n<br />\n請睇睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兄弟不必嘈交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />77照出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再討論武漢"},{"pid":"3125373843fa774dc22648ff801d5faace334c0a","tid":1286820,"uid":66784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:38:38.000Z","msg":"中亞穆斯林進駐新疆，唔單止消耗維穩經費同維穩人員條命<br />\n仲可以打擊一帶一路<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1262410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1262410&d=J%2B7a%2Fy